  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to see messages in full on the \"Sign Message\" screen. \r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\nAny message longer than one line is cut off, forcing user to scroll within the element. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nText box should auto-resize to fit the length of the message, up to some maximum height. \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe size of the text box is static and messages are hard to read.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15470435/39861223-3580079c-5440-11e8-89a4-f393d94034b1.jpeg\" width=\"300\" />\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15470435/39861215-3071e14e-5440-11e8-9f8f-1e29b58eacd4.jpeg\" width=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Opensea\r\n- Explore the sea\r\n- Buy an item\r\n- Sign transaction\r\n- Enter email address and name\r\n- Submit to load \"Sign message\" screen\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n*Summary*: \r\n\r\nAuto-expand message element on \"Sign message\" screen.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: https://i.diawi.com/G8ccM5\r\n* Operating System: iOS6s+\r\n\r\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://i.diawi.com/G8ccM5\">Install - Diawi - Development and In-house Apps Wireless Installation</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
